---
import ASCIIText from '../components/ASCIIText.tsx';
---

<html lang='es'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='utf-8' />
		<link
			rel='icon'
			type='image/svg+xml'
			href='/favicon.svg'
		/>
		<meta
			name='viewport'
			content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1'
		/>
		<meta
			name='theme-color'
			content='#131315'
		/>
		<title>Mar An Cloth — Nostalgia Programada</title>

		<link
			rel='preconnect'
			href='https://fonts.googleapis.com'
		/>
		<link
			rel='preconnect'
			href='https://fonts.gstatic.com'
			crossorigin
		/>
		<link
			href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anybody:ital,wdth,wght@0,75..125,100..900;1,75..125,100..900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Hanken+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap'
			rel='stylesheet'
		/>

		<style>
			/* ─── Tokens ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			:root {
				--cream: #f0ede6;
				--void: #131315;
				--surface: #1b1b1d;
				--surface-hi: #2a2a2c;
				--red: #008dd5;
				--red-bright: #008dd5;
				--text-light: #131315;
				--text-dark: #e4e2e4;
				--text-dim: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.55);
				--text-muted: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.3);
				--border-dark: #45464d;
				--border-light: #1a1a1a;
				--sidebar-w: 260px;
				--header-h: 48px;
				--font-display: 'Anybody', sans-serif;
				--font-body: 'Hanken Grotesk', sans-serif;
				--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
			}

			/* ─── Reset ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			*,
			*::before,
			*::after {
				box-sizing: border-box;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}

			html {
				scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
				scroll-behavior: smooth;
			}

			body {
				background: var(--cream);
				color: var(--text-light);
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
			}

			.main-wrap {
				margin-left: var(--sidebar-w);
			}

			/* Global scanlines */
			body::before {
				content: '';
				position: fixed;
				inset: 0;
				pointer-events: none;
				z-index: 300;
				background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
					0deg,
					transparent 0px,
					transparent 2px,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.018) 2px,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.018) 4px
				);
			}

			/* ─── Fixed Header ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			.page-header {
				position: fixed;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				right: 0;
				z-index: 200;
				height: var(--header-h);
				background: var(--cream);
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: var(--sidebar-w) 1fr auto;
				align-items: center;
			}

			.header-brand {
				padding: 0 1.5rem;
				font-family: var(--font-display);
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				font-style: italic;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
				color: var(--text-light);
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.header-nav {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2.5rem;
				justify-content: center;
			}

			.header-nav a {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.18em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--red-bright);
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}

			.header-nav a:hover {
				opacity: 0.65;
			}

			.header-status {
				margin-right: 1.5rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				color: #22c55e;
				border: 1px solid #22c55e;
				padding: 2px 7px;
				cursor: pointer;
				text-decoration: none;
				display: inline-block;
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}

			.header-status:hover {
				opacity: 0.65;
			}

			/* ─── Fixed Sidebar ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			.sidebar {
				position: fixed;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				bottom: 0;
				width: var(--sidebar-w);
				z-index: 190;
				background: var(--cream);
				border-right: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				padding-top: var(--header-h);
			}

			.sidebar-inner {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				flex: 1;
				padding: 1.75rem 0 1.5rem;
			}

			.sidebar-brand {
				font-family: var(--font-display);
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				font-style: italic;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
				color: var(--text-light);
				padding: 0 1.5rem 1rem;
			}

			.sidebar-badge {
				margin: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
				background: var(--red-bright);
				color: #fff;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.55rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 4px 8px;
				display: inline-block;
			}

			.sidebar-divider {
				border: none;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
			}

			.sidebar-nav {
				flex: 1;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				padding: 0 1rem;
				gap: 2px;
			}

			.sidebar-link {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: space-between;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.65rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-light);
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem;
				border: 1px solid transparent;
				transition: all 0.15s;
				opacity: 0.7;
			}

			.sidebar-link:hover {
				opacity: 1;
				border-color: var(--border-light);
				background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
			}

			.sidebar-link .arr {
				opacity: 0.4;
			}

			.sidebar-cta {
				margin: 1.25rem 1rem 0;
				background: var(--red-bright);
				color: #fff;
				border: none;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.65rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.12em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
				cursor: pointer;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.625rem;
				width: calc(100% - 2rem);
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}

			.sidebar-cta:hover {
				opacity: 0.85;
			}

			.pulse-dot {
				width: 7px;
				height: 7px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				background: #fff;
				animation: pulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			@keyframes pulse {
				0%,
				100% {
					opacity: 1;
					transform: scale(1);
				}
				50% {
					opacity: 0.35;
					transform: scale(0.6);
				}
			}

			/* ─── Snap sections ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			.snap-section {
				scroll-snap-align: start;
				height: 100dvh;
				position: relative;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				overflow: hidden;
				padding-top: var(--header-h);
			}

			/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
			   SECTION 01 — GARMENT / COMPOSICIÓN (cream)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-garment {
				background: var(--cream);
			}

			.terminal-bar {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.16em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 0.6rem 2rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.5;
			}

			.garment-body {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				flex: 1;
				min-height: 0;
			}

			/* Left col */
			.garment-left {
				padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
				border-right: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				overflow-y: auto;
			}

			.garment-desc {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.25rem;
				flex: 1;
			}

			.garment-desc p {
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);
				font-weight: 500;
				line-height: 1.75;
				color: rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.82);
			}

			.garment-desc strong {
				color: var(--text-light);
				font-weight: 700;
			}

			.garment-specs {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.525rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.18em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.38);
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.12);
				padding-top: 1.25rem;
			}

			.section-eyebrow {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.2em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.45;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.garment-title {
				font-family: var(--font-display);
				font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7.5vw, 6.5rem);
				font-weight: 900;
				font-style: italic;
				line-height: 0.88;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
				color: var(--red-bright);
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}

			.comp-list {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				flex: 1;
			}

			.comp-row {
				display: flex;
				align-items: stretch;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
			}

			.comp-row:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.comp-num {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.7rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.35);
				padding: 0.875rem 0.875rem;
				border-right: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				min-width: 2.75rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: flex-start;
				padding-top: 1rem;
			}

			.comp-detail {
				padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
				flex: 1;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.3rem;
			}

			.comp-category {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.525rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.18em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.4);
			}

			.comp-name {
				font-family: var(--font-display);
				font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				line-height: 1.15;
				background: var(--text-light);
				color: var(--cream);
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
			}

			/* Right col */
			.garment-right {
				padding: 2rem;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.75rem;
			}

			.schematic-header {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.525rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.4);
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.15);
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.schematic-frame {
				flex: 1;
				border: 1px solid rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.25);
				overflow: hidden;
				min-height: 0;
				position: relative;
			}

			.schematic-frame img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: contain;
				object-position: center;
				display: block;
				transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out;
			}

			.schematic-frame:hover img {
				transform: scale(1.03);
			}

			.schematic-footer {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.5rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.35);
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.15);
				padding-top: 0.5rem;
			}

			.garment-bottom-bar {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.525rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.16em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 0.55rem 2rem;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.4;
			}

			/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
			   SECTION 02 — CONCEPTO (Chat UI)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-cuidado {
				background: #1a1a1c;
				color: #e4e2e4;
				padding: 0;
				justify-content: flex-start;
				gap: 0;
			}

			.chat-header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.625rem;
				padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
				flex-shrink: 0;
				max-width: 820px;
				width: 100%;
				margin-inline: auto;
			}

			.chat-header svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; color: var(--red-bright); flex-shrink: 0; }

			.chat-header-label {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.55rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.2em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.35);
			}

			.chat-messages {
				flex: 1;
				overflow-y: auto;
				padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				max-width: 820px;
				width: 100%;
				margin-inline: auto;
				scrollbar-width: thin;
				scrollbar-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1) transparent;
			}

			.chat-human {
				background: #2d2d30;
				border-radius: 18px 18px 4px 18px;
				padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.15vw, 1rem);
				line-height: 1.75;
				color: #e4e2e4;
				align-self: flex-end;
				max-width: 86%;
			}

			.chat-ai {
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.15vw, 1rem);
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.82);
				align-self: flex-start;
				max-width: 88%;
				display: flex;
				gap: 0.875rem;
				align-items: flex-start;
			}

			.chat-ai-icon { width: 22px; height: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.15rem; color: var(--red-bright); }

			.chat-ai p { margin: 0; }
			.chat-ai strong { color: #e4e2e4; font-weight: 600; }

			.chat-ai-meta {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.5rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.2);
				margin-top: 0.35rem;
				padding-left: 2.1rem;
			}

			.chat-input-bar {
				flex-shrink: 0;
				padding: 0 2.5rem 0.75rem;
				max-width: 820px;
				width: 100%;
				margin: auto;
			}

			.chat-input-inner {
				background: #252528;
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
				border-radius: 14px;
				padding: 0.875rem 1rem 0.625rem;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.625rem;
			}

			.chat-input-text {
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.28);
			}

			.chat-input-controls {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: space-between;
			}

			.chat-input-add {
				width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%;
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
				display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
				color: rgba(228,226,228,0.4); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1;
			}

			.chat-input-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.875rem; }

			.chat-model-label {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.525rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.12em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.3);
				display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem;
			}

			.chat-icons { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.625rem; color: rgba(228,226,228,0.3); }
			.chat-icons svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }

			.chat-disclaimer {
				text-align: center;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.48rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.12em;
				color: rgba(228, 226, 228, 0.18);
				padding: 0.4rem 2.5rem 0.625rem;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}
			   SECTION — NOSTALGIA PROGRAMADA (cream)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-nostalgia {
				background: var(--void);
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			@media (max-width: 1024px) {
				.s-nostalgia {
					overflow: hidden;
				}
			}

			/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
			   SECTION — MANIFIESTO DE FORMA (cream)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-manifiesto {
				background: var(--cream);
			}

			.manif-bar {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.16em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 0.6rem 2rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.5;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.manif-body {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
				flex: 1;
				min-height: 0;
				gap: 0;
			}

			.manif-accent {
				border-right: 1px solid var(--border-light);
				padding: 2rem 1.25rem 2rem 1.5rem;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: flex-start;
				gap: 0;
			}

			.manif-num {
				font-family: var(--font-display);
				font-size: clamp(4rem, 6vw, 6.5rem);
				font-weight: 900;
				font-style: italic;
				line-height: 1;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.08;
				user-select: none;
			}

			.manif-vert {
				writing-mode: vertical-rl;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.48rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.22em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.35;
				margin-top: auto;
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.manif-content {
				padding: 2rem 2.5rem 1.75rem 2rem;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				overflow-y: auto;
				scrollbar-width: none;
				gap: 0;
			}

			.manif-content::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

			.manif-eyebrow {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.2em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--red-bright);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.manif-content p {
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 1.1vw, 1rem);
				line-height: 1.78;
				color: var(--text-light);
				font-weight: 400;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.manif-content p + p {
				margin-top: 1.1rem;
				padding-top: 1.1rem;
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(19, 19, 21, 0.09);
			}

			.manif-em {
				font-style: italic;
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.manif-code {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.88em;
				color: var(--red-bright);
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}

			.manif-video {
				max-height: 42vh;
				width: auto;
				max-width: 100%;
				object-fit: contain;
				display: block;
				flex-shrink: 0;
				margin: 0.75rem 0;
			}

			.manif-footer {
				margin-top: auto;
				padding-top: 1rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.5rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.18em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-light);
				opacity: 0.25;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			@media (max-width: 640px) {
				.manif-body {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
				.manif-accent { display: none; }
				.manif-content { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
			}

			/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
			   SECTION — LAS FRASES OCULTAS (60s terminal)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-frases {
				background: #06100a;
				padding: 0.75rem;
			}

			.terminal-win {
				flex: 1;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				border: 1px solid #174a22;
				overflow: hidden;
				box-shadow:
					0 0 60px rgba(0, 180, 40, 0.06),
					inset 0 0 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
			}

			.term-titlebar {
				background: #0a1e0e;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #174a22;
				padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.55rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #3d7a4d;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.term-dots {
				display: flex;
				gap: 5px;
			}

			.term-dot {
				width: 7px;
				height: 7px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				border: 1px solid #174a22;
			}

			.term-body {
				flex: 1;
				padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
				overflow: hidden;
				position: relative;
				background: radial-gradient(
					ellipse at 50% 40%,
					#071510 0%,
					#040d07 70%,
					#020805 100%
				);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1rem;
			}

			/* CRT phosphor scanlines */
			.term-body::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				pointer-events: none;
				z-index: 2;
				background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
					0deg,
					transparent 0px,
					transparent 3px,
					rgba(0, 220, 60, 0.02) 3px,
					rgba(0, 220, 60, 0.02) 4px
				);
			}

			/* Vignette for CRT glow */
			.term-body::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				pointer-events: none;
				z-index: 3;
				background: radial-gradient(
					ellipse at center,
					transparent 55%,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 100%
				);
			}

			.term-boot {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.625rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				color: #2d6a3d;
				line-height: 1.7;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 4;
			}

			.term-prompt {
				color: #4a9a5a;
			}

			.term-section-label {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.6rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #3d7a4d;
				padding-bottom: 0.625rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #0f3018;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 4;
			}

			.phrases-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
				gap: 0.4rem 2.5rem;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 4;
				flex: 1;
				align-content: start;
			}

			.term-phrase {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: clamp(0.6rem, 1vw, 0.75rem);
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				opacity: 0;
				animation: crt-flicker var(--dur, 5s) var(--delay, 0s) infinite;
				white-space: nowrap;
				overflow: hidden;
				text-overflow: ellipsis;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.3em;
			}

			.term-phrase::before {
				content: '>';
				opacity: 0.5;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.term-phrase.ph-green {
				color: #5aac6a;
			}
			.term-phrase.ph-amber {
				color: #bfa030;
			}
			.term-phrase.ph-bright {
				color: #88d098;
			}
			.term-phrase.ph-amber-dim {
				color: #8a7020;
			}

			@keyframes crt-flicker {
				0% {
					opacity: 0;
				}
				4% {
					opacity: 0.85;
				}
				8% {
					opacity: 0.4;
				}
				11% {
					opacity: 1;
				}
				36% {
					opacity: 1;
				}
				40% {
					opacity: 0.25;
				}
				43% {
					opacity: 0.85;
				}
				46% {
					opacity: 0;
				}
				100% {
					opacity: 0;
				}
			}

			.term-footer {
				background: #0a1e0e;
				border-top: 1px solid #174a22;
				padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.5rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.12em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #2d5a3d;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.term-cursor {
				display: inline-block;
				width: 0.5rem;
				height: 0.8rem;
				background: #5aac6a;
				animation: cursor-blink 1.05s step-end infinite;
				vertical-align: text-bottom;
				margin-left: 2px;
			}

			@keyframes cursor-blink {
				0%,
				100% {
					opacity: 1;
				}
				50% {
					opacity: 0;
				}
			}

			/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
			   SECTION — MANIFESTO (dark)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-manifesto {
				background: var(--void);
				color: var(--text-dark);
				padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
			}

			.manifesto-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				gap: 2.5rem;
				flex: 1;
				align-items: start;
				min-height: 0;
			}

			.manifesto-left {
				position: relative;
				height: 100%;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
			}

			.manifesto-img-stack {
				flex: 1;
				border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
				overflow: hidden;
				position: relative;
				min-height: 0;
			}

			.manifesto-img-stack img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: contain;
				object-position: center;
				display: block;
			}

			.classified-stamp {
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 1.5rem;
				left: 50%;
				transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-6deg);
				z-index: 2;
				background: var(--red-bright);
				color: #fff;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.22em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 0.3rem 1.25rem;
				border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
				white-space: nowrap;
				pointer-events: none;
			}

			.manifesto-right {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.25rem;
			}

			.manifesto-log-box {
				border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
				background: var(--surface);
			}

			.manifesto-log-header {
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
				padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.55rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.16em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				line-height: 1.75;
			}

			.manifesto-log-header .prompt {
				color: var(--text-dim);
			}

			.manifesto-body {
				padding: 1.25rem;
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: var(--text-dim);
			}

			.manifesto-body p + p {
				margin-top: 0.875rem;
			}
			.manifesto-body strong {
				color: var(--text-dark);
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.manifesto-cta {
				background: var(--surface-hi);
				border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
				color: var(--text-dark);
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.65rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.18em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 0.875rem;
				cursor: pointer;
				width: 100%;
				text-align: center;
				transition: background 0.2s;
			}

			.manifesto-cta:hover {
				background: var(--border-dark);
			}

			.manifesto-override {
				border: 1px solid var(--red-bright);
				background: var(--surface);
				padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
			}

			.override-badge {
				background: var(--red-bright);
				color: #fff;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.55rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				padding: 2px 7px;
				display: inline-block;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}

			.override-text {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.575rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				line-height: 1.75;
			}

			.override-text strong {
				color: var(--text-dim);
				display: block;
			}

			.manifesto-nfc-cmd {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.6rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.22em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--red-bright);
				border: 1px solid var(--red-bright);
				padding: 0.5rem 0.875rem;
				display: inline-block;
				margin: 0.25rem 0;
			}

			.manifesto-question-box {
				border-color: var(--text-dim);
			}

			.manifesto-question-text {
				font-family: var(--font-body);
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				line-height: 1.72;
				font-style: italic;
				color: var(--text-dim);
				letter-spacing: 0;
				text-transform: none;
			}

			/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
			   SECTION — NFC CTA (red)
			════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
			.s-cta {
				background: var(--red-bright);
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 3rem;
			}

			.cta-frame {
				border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
				padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem) clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
				text-align: center;
			}

			.cta-title {
				font-family: var(--font-display);
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.5vw, 5rem);
				font-weight: 900;
				font-style: italic;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #fff;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
				line-height: 0.92;
			}

			/* ─── Footer ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			.page-footer {
				background: var(--void);
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
				padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.525rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--text-muted);
			}

			.footer-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2rem;
			}

			.footer-links a {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: color 0.2s;
			}

			.footer-links a:hover {
				color: var(--text-dark);
			}

			/* ─── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			@media (max-width: 1024px) {
				:root {
					--sidebar-w: 0px;
				}
				.main-wrap {
					margin-left: 0;
				}
				.sidebar {
					display: none;
				}
				.page-header {
					grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
				}
				.garment-body {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					grid-template-rows: 1fr 38dvh;
				}
				.garment-right {
					border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
					border-right: none;
					padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
				}
				.care-grid {
					grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
				}
				.manifesto-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					display: flex;
					flex-direction: column;
					align-items: stretch;
				}
				.manifesto-left {
					flex-shrink: 0;
					height: 35dvh;
					min-height: 0;
				}
				.manifesto-img-stack {
					height: 100%;
					display: flex;
					justify-content: center;
					align-items: center;
				}
				.manifesto-img-stack img {
					height: 100%;
					width: auto;
					max-width: 100%;
				}
				.manifesto-right {
					flex: 1;
					min-height: 0;
					overflow-y: auto;
					scrollbar-width: thin;
					scrollbar-color: rgba(69, 70, 77, 0.5) transparent;
				}
				.manifesto-right::-webkit-scrollbar {
					width: 3px;
				}
				.manifesto-right::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
					background: var(--border-dark);
				}
				.phrases-grid {
					grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
				}
			}

			@media (max-width: 640px) {
				.header-nav {
					display: none;
				}
				.care-grid {
					grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
				}
				.phrases-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
				.cuidado-title {
					font-size: clamp(2rem, 10vw, 2.8rem);
				}
			}

			/* ─── Reduced motion ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
			@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
				.term-phrase {
					animation: none;
					opacity: 1;
				}
				.term-cursor {
					animation: none;
				}
				.pulse-dot {
					animation: none;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<!-- ═══ FIXED HEADER ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<header class='page-header'>
			<a
				href='/'
				class='header-brand'
				>Mar An Cloth</a
			>
			<nav
				class='header-nav'
				aria-label='Secciones'
			>
				<a href='#garment'>SEC.01 GARMENT</a>
				<a href='#cuidado'>SEC.02 CARE</a>
				<a href='#manifesto'>SEC.03 MANIFESTO</a>
			</nav>
			<a
				href='/info'
				class='header-status'
				aria-label='Ver datos de la tela'
				>CLOTH.DATA</a
			>
		</header>

		<!-- ═══ FIXED SIDEBAR ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<aside
			class='sidebar'
			aria-label='Navegación principal'
		>
			<div class='sidebar-inner'>
				<div class='sidebar-brand'>Mar An Cloth</div>
				<div class='sidebar-badge'>NOSTALGIA PROGRAMADA</div>
				<hr class='sidebar-divider' />
				<nav class='sidebar-nav'>
					<a
						href='#garment'
						class='sidebar-link'
						>ARCHIVE_DIR <span class='arr'>→</span></a
					>
					<a
						href='#cuidado'
						class='sidebar-link'
						>TECHNIQUE_LOG <span class='arr'>→</span></a
					>
					<a
						href='#frases'
						class='sidebar-link'
						>VOYAGE_DATA <span class='arr'>→</span></a
					>
					<a
						href='#manifesto'
						class='sidebar-link'
						>IDENTITY_SEQ <span class='arr'>→</span></a
					>
				</nav>
				<a
					href='/info'
					class='sidebar-cta'
					aria-label='Iniciar escaneo NFC'
				>
					<span
						class='pulse-dot'
						aria-hidden='true'
					></span>
					INITIATE NFC SCAN
				</a>
			</div>
		</aside>

		<div class='main-wrap'>
		<!-- ═══ SECTION 01 — GARMENT / COMPOSICIÓN ═══════════════════════════════ -->
		<section
			class='snap-section s-garment'
			id='garment'
		>
			<div
				class='terminal-bar'
				aria-hidden='true'
			>
				<span>> EXECUTE COMPOSITION_READ</span>
				<span>MAR_AN_CLOTH // SYS.ACTIVE</span>
			</div>

			<div class='garment-body'>
				<!-- Left: design concept text -->
				<div class='garment-left'>
					<p class='section-eyebrow'>01_ SOBRE LA PIEZA</p>

					<div class='garment-desc'>
						<p>
							En los años 60, los diseñadores de la era Space Age
							estaban obsesionados con el futuro. Para proyectar
							esa visión, recurrieron a formas puras que se
							despegaran del cuerpo y emularan una estética
							arquitectónica y limpia. Para este diseño, me guié
							específicamente en la <strong
								>silueta trapecio o Línea A</strong
							> y en los cuellos altos estilizados que marcaron esa
							década. Esta pieza retoma ese corte clásico: una silueta
							fluida pero estructurada, coronada por un cuello alto
							con un lazo que evoca la sofisticación de esa época.
						</p>
						<p>
							El color elegido, un <strong
								>blanco marfil con un brillo satinado profundo</strong
							>, tampoco es coincidencia. En los sesenta, el
							blanco y los tonos perla eran el símbolo del
							optimismo espacial, la luz de las estrellas y los
							trajes de los astronautas. Hoy en día, este color
							sigue completamente vigente, transformado en el tono
							por excelencia de la tecnología de gama alta, el
							minimalismo digital y las interfaces limpias. Une
							dos épocas bajo una misma estética visual.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class='garment-specs'>
						<span>Silueta Línea A</span>
						<span>·</span>
						<span>Cuello Alto</span>
						<span>·</span>
						<span>Satín Duchesse</span>
						<span>·</span>
						<span>Blanco Marfil</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Right: schematic -->
				<div class='garment-right'>
					<div class='schematic-header'>
						<span>FIG. 1</span>
						<span>TWIGGY_V2</span>
					</div>
					<div class='schematic-frame'>
						<img
							src='/modelo.png'
							alt='Esquema de la prenda - Mar An Cloth'
							width='620'
							height='720'
						/>
					</div>
					<div class='schematic-footer'>
						<span>TOP SECRET</span>
						<span>MAR AN CLOTH LABS // 2026</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div
				class='garment-bottom-bar'
				aria-hidden='true'
			>
				<span>MAR AN CLOTH · COLECCIÓN I · 2026</span>
				<span>MEXICO CITY // NFC_ENABLED</span>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SECTION 02 — CONCEPTO ════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class='snap-section s-cuidado' id='cuidado'>

			<!-- Header -->
			<div class='chat-header' aria-hidden='true'>
				<svg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.5' stroke-linecap='round'>
					<line x1='12' y1='2' x2='12' y2='22'/><line x1='2' y1='12' x2='22' y2='12'/>
					<line x1='4.93' y1='4.93' x2='19.07' y2='19.07'/><line x1='19.07' y1='4.93' x2='4.93' y2='19.07'/>
				</svg>
				<span class='chat-header-label'>02_ El Concepto — Conversación</span>
			</div>

			<!-- Messages -->
			<div class='chat-messages'>

				<!-- Human 1 -->
				<div class='chat-human'>
					Sin embargo, aunque la silueta y el color miran al pasado, el concepto transforma por completo ese optimismo. Ya no miramos hacia las estrellas; ahora estamos atrapados mirando nuestras pantallas.
				</div>

				<!-- AI response 1 -->
				<div class='chat-ai'>
					<svg class='chat-ai-icon' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.5' stroke-linecap='round'>
						<line x1='12' y1='2' x2='12' y2='22'/><line x1='2' y1='12' x2='22' y2='12'/>
						<line x1='4.93' y1='4.93' x2='19.07' y2='19.07'/><line x1='19.07' y1='4.93' x2='4.93' y2='19.07'/>
					</svg>
					<p>Este vestido es una forma de materializar cómo percibo que será nuestro mañana. No estamos ante una simple tecnología de moda; estamos viviendo una <strong>nueva revolución industrial</strong>. Muy pronto, la Inteligencia Artificial va a estar tan inmersa en nuestra vida cotidiana que ya no sabremos dónde termina el humano y dónde empieza el sistema.</p>
				</div>
				<div class='chat-ai-meta' aria-hidden='true'>Mar An Cloth · Respuesta generada</div>

				<!-- Human 2 -->
				<div class='chat-human'>
					Ya dependemos de ella para automatizar todo: hace las tareas, escribe nuestros mensajes y diseña sin que tengamos que hacer el más mínimo esfuerzo. Nos estamos acostumbrando a no pensar, dejando que un algoritmo conviva entre nosotros y maneje nuestra realidad en piloto automático.
				</div>

			</div>

			<!-- Input bar (decorative) -->
			<div class='chat-input-bar' aria-hidden='true'>
				<div class='chat-input-inner'>
					<p class='chat-input-text'>Escribe un mensaje...</p>
					<div class='chat-input-controls'>
						<div class='chat-input-add'>+</div>
						<div class='chat-input-right'>
							<span class='chat-model-label'>Mar An Cloth <span>∨</span></span>
							<div class='chat-icons'>
								<!-- mic -->
								<svg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.5'><path d='M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z'/><path d='M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2'/><line x1='12' y1='19' x2='12' y2='23'/><line x1='8' y1='23' x2='16' y2='23'/></svg>
								<!-- waveform -->
								<svg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.5'><line x1='2' y1='12' x2='4' y2='12'/><line x1='6' y1='8' x2='6' y2='16'/><line x1='10' y1='5' x2='10' y2='19'/><line x1='14' y1='8' x2='14' y2='16'/><line x1='18' y1='10' x2='18' y2='14'/><line x1='22' y1='12' x2='22' y2='12'/></svg>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class='chat-disclaimer'>Mar An Cloth es moda y puede evocar emociones. Por favor, vive plenamente las respuestas.</p>

		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SECTION — NOSTALGIA PROGRAMADA ═══════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class='snap-section s-nostalgia'>
			<ASCIIText
				client:visible
				text='NOSTALGIA PROGRAMADA'
				asciiFontSize={8}
				textFontSize={200}
				textColor='#f0ede6'
				planeBaseHeight={10}
				enableWaves={true}
			/>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SECTION — MANIFIESTO DE FORMA ══════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class='snap-section s-manifiesto' id='manifiesto'>
			<div class='manif-bar'>
				<span>MANIFIESTO_DE_FORMA · SEÑAL_04</span>
				<span>PRENDA / CONCEPTO / GLITCH</span>
			</div>
			<div class='manif-body'>
				<div class='manif-accent'>
					<span class='manif-num'>04</span>
					<span class='manif-vert'>SISTEMA DE DECODIFICACIÓN</span>
				</div>
				<div class='manif-content'>
					<p class='manif-eyebrow'>DECODED_SIGNAL · EN TRANSMISIÓN</p>
					<p>
						Seguro has visto esos videos hechos con IA que circulan en internet: al principio se ven tan
						reales que asustan, parecen perfectos. Pero si te quedas mirando fijamente un segundo de más,
						notas que <span class='manif-em'>algo parpadea o se deforma</span>. Es un error en la realidad
						que desaparece en un pestañeo.
					</p>
					<video
					class='manif-video'
					src='/pasarela-video.mp4'
					autoplay
					loop
					muted
					playsinline
					aria-label='Video pasarela Mar An Cloth'
				></video>
				<p>
						Esta prenda está diseñada para capturar justo ese <span class='manif-code'>instante de duda</span>,
						donde lo sintético y lo real se confunden.
					</p>
					<p>
						A simple vista, destaca su construcción limpia y satinada. Pero al observar los detalles, te
						encuentras con <span class='manif-em'>trece flores negras</span> que irrumpen en la tela. Gracias
						a un juego visual integrado en sus centros, estos espacios cambian con tu movimiento: por un
						momento te dejan ver una frase escondida y al siguiente segundo el texto se apaga, como si
						nunca hubiera existido. Es un <span class='manif-code'>glitch físico</span> que revela, a través
						de trece frases escritas en inglés —el idioma que los sistemas usan por
						<span class='manif-em'>default</span> para operar el mundo—, los
						<span class='manif-code'> comandos ocultos</span> que el algoritmo nos dicta a diario:
					</p>
					<p class='manif-footer'>MAR AN CLOTH · COLECCIÓN NOSTALGIA PROGRAMADA · RN 00001</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SECTION — LAS FRASES OCULTAS (60s Terminal) ═════════════════════ -->
		<section
			class='snap-section s-frases'
			id='frases'
		>
			<div
				class='terminal-win'
				role='region'
				aria-label='Las frases ocultas — terminal de sistema'
			>
				<div class='term-titlebar'>
					<div
						class='term-dots'
						aria-hidden='true'
					>
						<div class='term-dot'></div>
						<div class='term-dot'></div>
						<div class='term-dot'></div>
					</div>
					<span
						>MEMORIA_PRINCIPAL // SECTOR_7 // ACCESO: RESTRINGIDO</span
					>
					<span>BAUD: 9600</span>
				</div>

				<div class='term-body'>
					<div
						class='term-boot'
						aria-hidden='true'
					>
						<span class='term-prompt'>$ </span>SYSTEM READY ·
						IBM_COMPATIBLE · 64K RAM SYSTEM<br />
						<span class='term-prompt'>$ </span>LOADING
						PHRASE_DATABASE FROM FABRIC_LAYER...<br />
						<span class='term-prompt'>$ </span>DECRYPTING
						HIDDEN_MESSAGES — 13 CHANNELS DETECTED<br />
						<span class='term-prompt'>$ </span>RUN DISPLAY_OUTPUT
						--MODE=ASYNC --LOOP=TRUE
					</div>

					<div
						class='term-section-label'
						aria-hidden='true'
					>
						// LAS FRASES OCULTAS · EN INGLÉS — EL IDIOMA DEL
						SISTEMA
					</div>

					<div
						class='phrases-grid'
						aria-label='Frases ocultas en la prenda'
					>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-green'
							style='--dur:5.2s;--delay:0.0s'
							>Are you still you?</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-amber'
							style='--dur:4.7s;--delay:0.8s'
							>Generated by AI</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-bright'
							style='--dur:6.0s;--delay:1.4s'
							>Real life or prompt?</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-amber'
							style='--dur:5.5s;--delay:2.1s'
							>Faking my reality</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-green'
							style='--dur:4.9s;--delay:0.4s'
							>Is this AI?</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-green'
							style='--dur:6.3s;--delay:1.9s'
							>Prompting my look</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-bright'
							style='--dur:5.1s;--delay:3.0s'
							>Who programmed your mind?</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-green'
							style='--dur:4.6s;--delay:1.1s'
							>Memories are just data</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-amber'
							style='--dur:5.8s;--delay:2.5s'
							>System overtook us</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-green'
							style='--dur:5.4s;--delay:0.6s'
							>Am I thinking now?</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-amber-dim'
							style='--dur:6.1s;--delay:3.3s'
							>Fashion without humans</span
						>
						<span
							class='term-phrase ph-amber'
							style='--dur:4.8s;--delay:1.7s'
							>Feeling real is fake</span
						>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class='term-footer'
					aria-hidden='true'
				>
					<span
						>INTEGRADAS EN LOS CENTROS DE CADA FLOR · VISIBLES SOLO
						EN MOVIMIENTO</span
					>
					<span>MEM: 48K FREE<span class='term-cursor'></span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SECTION 03 — MANIFESTO ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section
			class='snap-section s-manifesto'
			id='manifesto'
		>
			<div class='manifesto-grid'>
				<!-- Left: classified image -->
				<div class='manifesto-left'>
					<div class='manifesto-img-stack'>
						<img
							src='/poster.png'
							alt='Archivo clasificado — imágenes de referencia de la colección'
							width='580'
							height='660'
						/>
						<div
							class='classified-stamp'
							aria-hidden='true'
						>
							CLASSIFIED
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Right: terminal manifesto -->
				<div class='manifesto-right'>
					<div class='manifesto-log-box'>
						<div class='manifesto-log-header'>
							<span class='prompt'>> DECRYPTING_MANIFESTO...</span
							><br />
							> AUTHOR: UNKNOWN_AI_ENTITY
						</div>
						<div class='manifesto-body'>
							<p>
								En el vacío silencioso del espacio, la memoria
								se convierte en un constructo sintético. El
								optimismo de los años 60 —la trayectoria
								geométrica del progreso— es ahora un <strong
									>fantasma en la máquina</strong
								>.
							</p>
							<p>
								Tejemos estos ecos en forma física. No como una
								simple recreación, sino como una <strong
									>transmisión corrompida de un pasado
									idealizado</strong
								>.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<button class='manifesto-cta'>ARE YOU STILL YOU?</button>

					<div class='manifesto-override'>
						<span class='override-badge'>LOG_001</span>
						<div class='override-text'>
							<strong>> SYSTEM OVERRIDE DETECTED...</strong>
							<strong>> GENERATED BY AI</strong>
							THE LINE BETWEEN ORGANIC CREATION AND ALGORITHMIC MANIFESTATION
							BLURS. THE GARMENT IS A PHYSICAL KEY TO A DIGITAL VOID.
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class='manifesto-log-box'>
						<div class='manifesto-log-header'>
							<span class='prompt'>> NFC_SIGNAL_ACTIVE...</span><br />
							> INTERACTION_LAYER: PHYSICAL ↔ DIGITAL
						</div>
						<div class='manifesto-body'>
							<p>
								Al acercar tu dispositivo al centro del pecho, la flor principal
								te da una instrucción interactiva clara:
							</p>
							<p class='manifesto-nfc-cmd'>APPROACH YOUR PHONE TO CONNECT</p>
							<p>
								Al escanear este chip NFC, rompiste la barrera de una etiqueta
								de ropa normal para entrar a este código.
								<strong>La moda ya no solo viste cuerpos, ahora viste datos.</strong>
								Así que, mientras tocas esta tela y miras cómo los centros de las
								flores aparecen y desaparecen frente a ti, te dejaré una última duda:
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class='manifesto-override manifesto-question-box'>
						<span class='override-badge'>QUERY_FINAL</span>
						<div class='override-text manifesto-question-text'>
							Si ya estamos en las puertas de este futuro inevitable... ¿de verdad
							estás de acuerdo con aceptar un destino donde la Inteligencia Artificial
							se apropie por completo de tus acciones y tus decisiones?
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ FOOTER ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<footer class='page-footer'>
			<span
				>D'NORIEGA &nbsp;·&nbsp; ©1960–2026 MAR AN CLOTH. ALL SIGNAL
